## 5. 常用查询命令

状态：`stable`

```powershell
rg -n "待确认|TODO|FIXME" AGENTS.md docs {{CODE_ROOT}}
Get-ChildItem {{OUTPUT_DIR}} -Recurse -File |
  Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending |
  Select-Object -First 30 FullName, LastWriteTime, Length
Get-ChildItem {{LOG_DIR}} -Recurse -File |
  Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending |
  Select-Object -First 30 FullName, LastWriteTime, Length
```

## 6. 文档完整性检查

```powershell
rg -n "\{\{[A-Z0-9_]+\}\}" AGENTS.md docs
git diff -- AGENTS.md docs
```

## 7. Git / worktree 安全命令

状态：`stable`

```powershell
git status --short --branch
git branch --show-current
git worktree list
git diff --stat
```

不要把 `git reset --hard`、强制 checkout 或历史重写写成常用命令。

